{"TopicId":216740,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Is it necessary to add a silver-white UI theme like in KSP1 to KSP2?","CreatedByName":"Meredith Nathaniei","CreatedById":225139,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-20T04:17:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Meredith Nathaniei","CreatedById":225139,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-20T04:17:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the actual gameplay, the black UI makes people very confused.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-27T20:31:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224274788\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216740\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221681964239\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225139\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meredith Nathaniei\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/20/2023 at 5:17 AM, Meredith Nathaniei said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the actual gameplay, the black UI makes people very confused.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow71","CreatedById":210112,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-28T00:52:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224274788\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216740\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221681964239\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225139\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meredith Nathaniei\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/19/2023 at 9:17 PM, Meredith Nathaniei said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the actual gameplay, the black UI makes people very confused.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProof for your statement?\u00A0 Or are you werely speculating?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Meredith Nathaniei","CreatedById":225139,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-30T15:57:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224277552\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216740\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221682643133\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210112\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Scarecrow71\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/28/2023 at 8:52 AM, Scarecrow71 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProof for your statement?\u00A0 Or are you werely speculating?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is probably the reason why I am not very sensitive to color, I personally feel that the white UI in KSP1 is more practical.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Scarecrow71","CreatedById":210112,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-30T16:41:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224278373\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216740\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221682870247\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225139\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Meredith Nathaniei\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n43 minutes ago, Meredith Nathaniei said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is probably the reason why I am not very sensitive to color, I personally feel that the white UI in KSP1 is more practical.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo then it\u0027s a personal thing as opposed to making people confused.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GalileOh-No","CreatedById":228006,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-30T17:28:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t really have a dog in the fight but what if the UI element colors (or dare I even mention fonts) were tweakable in the game options? Sounds like a mod (and/or accessibility feature) some folks would appreciate.\u00A0 Probably not the biggest fish to fry at present but, yeah, I\u0027d probably tune some of the defaults if I had the ability.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr at least that\u0027s how I interpreted your comment, Meridith: you yourself are not very sensitive to the default colors.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-30T17:35:37Z\u0022 title=\u002204/30/2023 05:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 30, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by GalileOh-No\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}